---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Friends / Links" description="Friend links, communities, tools, and stable resources.">
  <article class="article">
    <p class="eyebrow">Links</p>
    <h1>Friends / Links</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Here are the websites I follow and recommend, together with stable communities and resources that are useful
      enough to keep.
    </p>

    <h2>Friends | Links I Follow</h2>
    <div class="friend-links">
      <a class="friend-link" href="http://www.edwinjing-blog.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <img
          class="friend-link-avatar"
          src="https://api.dicebear.com/7.x/notionists/svg?seed=Edwin&amp;backgroundColor=f0f4f8"
          alt="Chen Jing avatar"
          width="48"
          height="48"
        />
        <span class="friend-link-body">
          <strong>Chen Jing</strong>
          <span>Be Global. Be Active.</span>
        </span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <h2>Research / Learning Communities</h2>
    <p>Resource links will be added when they become useful and stable.</p>

    <h2>Tools &amp; Resources</h2>
    <p>Resource links will be added when they become useful and stable.</p>

    <h2>Link Exchange</h2>
    <p>
      If you would like to exchange links, please make sure the site is suitable for public display and can stay
      available over time. Links will be added after confirmation.
    </p>

    <h2>Link Format</h2>
    <p>Please include the following four fields:</p>
    <pre><code>{`name: Site Name
url: https://site-url
avatar: https://avatar-url
desc: One-sentence introduction.`}</code></pre>

    <h2>Link Notes</h2>
    <p>
      Links are ordered by the time they are added. I may check link availability from time to time. If a website
      becomes unavailable, the link may be temporarily removed and restored later.
    </p>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .friend-links {
    display: grid;
    gap: 12px;
    margin: 18px 0 8px;
  }

  .friend-link {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 14px;
    background: var(--surface);
    color: var(--text);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .friend-link:hover {
    color: var(--text);
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .friend-link-avatar {
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: var(--bg);
  }

  .friend-link-body {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2px;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .friend-link-body span {
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  pre {
    overflow-x: auto;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 16px;
    background: var(--surface);
  }

  code {
    font-family: ui-monospace, "SFMono-Regular", Consolas, monospace;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
  }
</style>
